%% OAuth2 / Entra ID authentication + passwordless data access
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client / Service
    participant E as Microsoft Entra ID
    participant A as Node.js API (App Service)
    participant J as JWKS (Entra keys)
    participant K as Key Vault
    participant S as Azure SQL

    C->>E: Request token (auth code or client_credentials)
    E-->>C: Access token (JWT, aud=api://clientId)
    C->>A: GET /api/v1/items (Authorization Bearer JWT)
    A->>J: Fetch signing keys by kid (cached)
    J-->>A: Public key
    A->>A: Verify signature, iss, aud, exp and check scp or roles
    alt token invalid
        A-->>C: 401 Unauthorized
    else missing scope
        A-->>C: 403 Forbidden
    else authorized
        A->>K: Get secret (Managed Identity token)
        K-->>A: Secret value
        A->>S: Query (Managed Identity AAD access token)
        S-->>A: Rows
        A-->>C: 200 OK { featureFlag, items }
    end
